        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="1-安装jdk和tomcat"><a href="#1-安装jdk和tomcat" class="headerlink" title="1.安装jdk和tomcat"></a>1.安装jdk和tomcat</h4><ul><li>命令下载并解压<ul><li>待续。。。</li></ul></li><li>目录<ul><li><code>vim /etc/profile</code>:环境变量</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="2-配置"><a href="#2-配置" class="headerlink" title="2 配置"></a>2 配置</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#配置java环境</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#配置jre_home</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export JRE_HOME=$&#123;JAVA_HOME&#125;/jre</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export CLASSPATH=.:$JAVA_HOME/jre/lib/rt.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/dt.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/tools.jar</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">8</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># tomcathome</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">9</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export CATALINA_HOME=/usr/local/apache-tomcat8</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">10</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export PATH=$CATALINA_HOME/bin:$PATH</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-命令"><a href="#3-命令" class="headerlink" title="3 命令"></a>3 命令</h4><ul><li><code>cd</code>:切换目录</li><li><code>pwd</code>：打印所在路径</li><li>vim 目录：<ul><li>i:编辑</li><li><kbd>ESC</kbd>:退出</li><li>wq!:保存后退出</li><li>q!：不保存退出</li></ul></li><li><p>下载工具</p><ul><li>rpm</li><li>wget</li><li>yum</li></ul></li><li><p>添加软连接</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
