        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="1-1-NodeJs"><a href="#1-1-NodeJs" class="headerlink" title="1.1 NodeJs"></a>1.1 <a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.13.1/node-v12.13.1-x64.msi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NodeJs</a></h4><ul><li>1 <a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.13.1/node-v12.13.1-x64.msi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载安装</a> </li><li>2 查看是否安装成功：添加到环境变量；node —version：输出版本号</li></ul><h4 id="1-2-hexo或hexo-cli"><a href="#1-2-hexo或hexo-cli" class="headerlink" title="1.2 hexo或hexo-cli"></a>1.2 hexo或hexo-cli</h4><ul><li><p><code>npm install -g hexo</code></p><ul><li><p>失败   nodejs版本要求 &gt;8</p></li><li><p>解析错误：<code>npm set registry https://registry.npmjs.org/</code>（更改镜像源）</p></li></ul></li><li><p><code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code>:有效</p></li></ul><h4 id="1-3-git"><a href="#1-3-git" class="headerlink" title="1.3 git"></a>1.3 git</h4><p>下载并安装git</p><h4 id="1-4-初始化"><a href="#1-4-初始化" class="headerlink" title="1.4 初始化"></a>1.4 初始化</h4><p>拷贝原先的文件</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">_config.yml</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package.json</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scaffolds/</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source/</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">themes/</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">否则`hexo s`会失败</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---------------</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--------------</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">8</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-5-配置ssh"><a href="#1-5-配置ssh" class="headerlink" title="1.5 配置ssh"></a>1.5 配置ssh</h4><p>免密操作：</p><ul><li><p>1 <code>git config --global user.name &quot;mengki258&quot;</code></p></li><li><p>2 <code>git config --global user.email &quot;1710620635@qq.com&quot;</code></p></li><li><p>3 <code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;1710620635@qq.com&quot;</code></p><ul><li><p>输入密码：password</p></li><li><p>保存位置</p><blockquote><p>认证信息： C:\Users{username}/.ssh/id_rsa.</p><p>公钥：C:\Users{username}/.ssh/id_rsa.pub.</p></blockquote></li></ul></li><li><p>添加公钥到github的ssh上</p></li></ul><h4 id="1-6-保存到github"><a href="#1-6-保存到github" class="headerlink" title="1.6 保存到github"></a>1.6 保存到github</h4><p><code>hexo d</code></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
